{
  "stem": "18865.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And 10 days before the war started, my parents were able to leave.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was able to write, and they wrote back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We even were able to talk to each other two or three times over the telephone.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- still with the farmer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they arrived in-- they went to Slough, where I-- we had a relatives, close friends of my parents.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they rented an apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they lived there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they wanted-- and I wanted to go to them, because when the-- after the war, 10 days later, the war started.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I felt if the Germans come and-- I-- we-- I want to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We want to-- want to go all together if-- you know, if they bomb us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Sanderson wouldn't let me go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was committed to stay there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was not allowed to leave until they allowed it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She would not allow it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She wouldn't let me go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that made things even more difficult.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In their house?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nine months.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, finally, they had no choice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I-- I think there was a limit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have to stay in the area for-- for so long.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, finally, I said, I will stay here until you get someone else.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I will teach her what I know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then I went to Slough to live with my parents and my sister.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my sister-- we-- my sister and I went to school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we learned-- tried to learn shorthand and typing and English.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "By that time I spoke English pretty well, but I spoke it was a-- English-- English with a-- I had French.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I spoke fluent French before, with a French and German accent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was pretty messy.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
